 2023-03792023-04-28PWGSC
ActNational Capital Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Public Works and Government Services of ANDREAS (ANDY) KIKITES of Toronto, Ontario, to be a member of the Board of Directors of the National Capital Commission, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Michael Foderick, whose term has expired.
